1
00:00:06,966 --> 00:00:08,600
[ BIRDS TWITTERING ]

2
00:00:08,633 --> 00:00:10,300
[ GIRL ]
THE GARDEN OF AMAHARA?

3
00:00:10,333 --> 00:00:12,866
[ ELDERLY WOMAN ]
YES, SHIEMI.
HAVE YOU HEARD ABOUT IT?

4
00:00:12,900 --> 00:00:16,066
UH-UH. I DON'T LIKE
GOING OTHER PLACES.

5
00:00:16,100 --> 00:00:18,233
THEY SAY
IT'S GOD'S GARDEN,

6
00:00:18,266 --> 00:00:21,566
THE PLACE WHERE HE'S GATHERED
ALL THE PLANTS IN THE WORLD.

7
00:00:21,600 --> 00:00:25,633
AND IF YOU GO THERE,
YOU CAN SEE EVERY SINGLE PLANT
UNDER THE SUN.

8
00:00:25,666 --> 00:00:27,066
ISN'T THAT WONDERFUL?

9
00:00:27,100 --> 00:00:29,633
REALLY?
OH, I WANNA GO THERE.

10
00:00:29,666 --> 00:00:31,733
LET'S GO TOGETHER, GRANDMA.

11
00:00:31,766 --> 00:00:36,166
OH, I'D LIKE TO,
BUT I'M OLD NOW
AND MY LEGS HURT.

12
00:00:36,200 --> 00:00:38,966
BESIDES, THIS GARDEN
IS MY TREASURE,

13
00:00:39,000 --> 00:00:41,066
AND I COULD
NEVER LEAVE IT BEHIND.

14
00:00:41,100 --> 00:00:42,466
THAT WOULDN'T DO.

15
00:00:42,500 --> 00:00:44,366
BUT WHEN YOU'RE
ALL GROWN UP, SHIEMI,

16
00:00:44,400 --> 00:00:46,766
MAYBE YOU COULD
GO LOOK FOR IT.

17
00:00:46,800 --> 00:00:48,666
MM-HMM.

18
00:00:58,000 --> 00:01:01,266
♪ [ MAN SINGING
IN JAPANESE ]

19
00:02:21,900 --> 00:02:23,733
[ CRYING ]

20
00:02:25,967 --> 00:02:30,733
I DON'T BELIEVE IT.
IT'S SO... SAD.

21
00:02:30,767 --> 00:02:34,300
- RIN.
- HEY! GIVE IT BACK,
DAMN IT!

22
00:02:34,333 --> 00:02:37,067
I DON'T WANT YOU SOAKING
MY MANGA WITH YOUR WEIRD FLUIDS.

23
00:02:37,100 --> 00:02:39,367
YOU SHOULD BE STUDYING.
HAVE YOU EVEN LOOKED...

24
00:02:39,400 --> 00:02:41,567
AT ANY OF THE MATERIALS
I GAVE YOU YESTERDAY?

25
00:02:41,600 --> 00:02:45,067
I LOOKED AT 'EM.
OH, I LOOKED AT 'EM,
ALL RIGHT.

26
00:02:45,100 --> 00:02:47,133
BUT WHAT'S WITH THIS
"FOR KIDS" CRAP?

27
00:02:47,167 --> 00:02:49,933
DO YOU THINK I'M SOME KIND
OF MORON OR SOMETHING?

28
00:02:49,967 --> 00:02:51,900
NO, YOU'RE NOT A MORON.

29
00:02:51,933 --> 00:02:54,033
IDIOT, YES.
MORON, NO.

30
00:02:54,067 --> 00:02:56,467
[ GROWLS ]
MOLE-INFESTED, FOUR-EYED--

31
00:02:56,500 --> 00:02:58,667
I SIMPLY THOUGHT
THAT IF YOU STARTED WITH THOSE,

32
00:02:58,700 --> 00:03:01,633
THEY MIGHT BE A LITTLE EASIER
FOR YOU TO HANDLE.

33
00:03:01,667 --> 00:03:04,433
THAT'S ANOTHER THING.
DO YOU THINK
I'M THE TYPE OF GUY...

34
00:03:04,467 --> 00:03:06,933
WHO CAN SIT AT A DESK
AND FREAKING STUDY ALL DAY?

35
00:03:06,967 --> 00:03:09,067
NOT BY A LONG SHOT.
NOT YOU.

36
00:03:09,100 --> 00:03:11,067
THE THING IS, DO YOU WANT
TO BE AN EXORCIST?

37
00:03:11,100 --> 00:03:12,667
UH, WELL, YEAH.

38
00:03:12,700 --> 00:03:15,100
THEN HIT THE BOOKS
AND DO YOUR HOMEWORK.

39
00:03:15,133 --> 00:03:17,400
TAKE ADVANTAGE OF YOUR DAYS OFF.

40
00:03:17,433 --> 00:03:19,167
HEY, WHERE ARE YOU GOING?

41
00:03:19,200 --> 00:03:22,900
I GOT CALLED.
ALSO, I HAVE TO GET
SOME SUPPLIES.

42
00:03:22,933 --> 00:03:25,100
I WON'T BE GONE LONG.

43
00:03:25,133 --> 00:03:27,333
YOU GOT CALLED
FOR AN EXORCISM?

44
00:03:27,367 --> 00:03:30,133
MM-HMM.
I'M COMING WITH YOU.

45
00:03:30,167 --> 00:03:34,300
I CAN LEARN WAY MORE BY
WATCHING YOU THAN BY READING
ABOUT IT IN SOME OLD BOOK.

46
00:03:34,333 --> 00:03:36,867
BUT YOU'RE STILL
JUST A PAGE, RIN.

47
00:03:36,900 --> 00:03:39,867
I'M SORRY, BUT THEY DON'T ALLOW
TRAINEES OUT IN THE FIELD.

48
00:03:39,900 --> 00:03:41,467
[ GROANS ]
DON'T GIVE ME THAT.

49
00:03:41,500 --> 00:03:44,033
WHAT THE HELL DO THEY KNOW
ABOUT ANYTHING ANYWAY?

50
00:03:44,067 --> 00:03:46,000
I'M ALREADY
FIELD TESTED.

51
00:03:46,033 --> 00:03:49,067
YOU HAVE A POINT.
OKAY, BUT ONLY TO WATCH.

52
00:03:49,100 --> 00:03:51,233
KNEW YOU'D SEE IT MY WAY.

53
00:03:51,267 --> 00:03:55,933
DO WHAT I TELL YOU,
AND DON'T ANYTHING-- <i>ANYTHING--</i>
WITHOUT CHECKING WITH ME FIRST.

54
00:03:55,967 --> 00:03:57,967
I GOT IT, YUKIO,
LOUD AND CLEAR.

55
00:03:58,000 --> 00:04:00,633
THIS IS THE KEY
TO THE SUPPLY SHOP.

56
00:04:00,667 --> 00:04:05,033
IT'S ONE OF THE MANY KEYS
THAT ARE ISSUED
ONLY TO QUALIFIED EXORCISTS.

57
00:04:05,067 --> 00:04:07,333
LOOKS LIKE YOU'VE GOT
A WHOLE BOATLOAD OF 'EM.

58
00:04:09,767 --> 00:04:11,867
[ GASPS ]
WHOA.

59
00:04:16,000 --> 00:04:19,200
[ RIN ]
WHOA! THIS IS WAY HIGH!

60
00:04:22,333 --> 00:04:25,433
WHAT'S THE POINT OF HAVING KEYS
THAT ACT LIKE WARP ZONES?

61
00:04:25,467 --> 00:04:28,200
THE ACADEMY HAPPENS TO BE
AN IMPORTANT BASE
OF OPERATIONS...

62
00:04:28,233 --> 00:04:30,100
FOR THE KNIGHTS
OF THE TRUE CROSS.

63
00:04:30,133 --> 00:04:34,433
THE DIRECTOR'S POWER PROTECTS IT
FROM PRETTY MUCH ANY ATTACK
BY MID-LEVEL DEMONS.

64
00:04:34,467 --> 00:04:38,633
HE DOES IT USING A SERIES
OF TALISMANS, BARRIERS
AND EVEN LABYRINTHS.

65
00:04:38,667 --> 00:04:44,567
REALLY? I GUESS HE'S NOT
YOUR AVERAGE WHACKED-OUT CLOWN
AFTER ALL.

66
00:04:44,600 --> 00:04:46,467
AS LONG AS YOU HAVE
THE RIGHT KEY,

67
00:04:46,500 --> 00:04:50,067
YOU CAN GO ANYWHERE YOU WANT
IN THE SCHOOL WITHOUT GETTING
CAUGHT IN ONE OF HIS TRAPS.

68
00:04:50,100 --> 00:04:52,500
THAT SOUNDS CONVENIENT.

69
00:04:52,533 --> 00:04:54,600
[ YUKIO ]
KEYS ARE VERY IMPORTANT HERE.

70
00:04:54,633 --> 00:04:57,500
IF YOU GET ONE,
MAKE SURE YOU DON'T LOSE IT.

71
00:05:06,900 --> 00:05:10,567
OKAY. YOU HAVE TO WAIT HERE
WHILE I GO GET THE SUPPLIES.

72
00:05:10,600 --> 00:05:14,367
- I WANNA GO TOO.
- NO. THE STORE'S FOR EXORCISTS
AND HIGHER-UPS ONLY.

73
00:05:14,400 --> 00:05:17,200
- I WON'T BE LONG.
- [ GROWLS ]

74
00:05:18,733 --> 00:05:23,433
- DON'T GO ANYWHERE,
AND DON'T TOUCH ANYTHING.
- YEAH, I GOT IT!

75
00:05:23,467 --> 00:05:24,733
[ GROWLS ]

76
00:05:26,733 --> 00:05:29,900
GEEZ, NOW THAT HE'S
MR. BIG MAN ON CAMPUS,

77
00:05:29,933 --> 00:05:31,800
HE'S TREATING ME
LIKE A LITTLE KID.

78
00:05:31,833 --> 00:05:34,133
"DON'T GO ANYWHERE,
DON'T TOUCH ANYTHING."

79
00:05:34,167 --> 00:05:35,767
WHO DOES HE THINK HE IS,
MY MOM?

80
00:05:38,233 --> 00:05:43,533
JERK. ONE OF THESE DAYS,
HE'S GONNA BE THE ONE
THAT'S COUNTING ON ME.

81
00:05:43,567 --> 00:05:45,033
HUH?

82
00:05:45,067 --> 00:05:46,833
[ BIRDS TWITTERING ]

83
00:05:54,767 --> 00:05:57,033
[ WATER TRICKLING ]

84
00:05:57,067 --> 00:05:59,867
NO WAY!

85
00:05:59,900 --> 00:06:01,733
IT'S AWESOME IN THERE.

86
00:06:03,400 --> 00:06:04,733
HUH?

87
00:06:13,600 --> 00:06:14,867
[ GASPS ]

88
00:06:18,833 --> 00:06:20,900
- [ GASPS ]
- [ EXPLOSION ]

89
00:06:20,933 --> 00:06:22,733
[ CREAKING ]

90
00:06:24,667 --> 00:06:26,233
[ BOTH GASP ]

91
00:06:26,267 --> 00:06:29,933
UH, I DIDN'T DO IT.
IT JUST HAPPENED.

92
00:06:29,967 --> 00:06:32,567
HUH? DEMON!

93
00:06:32,600 --> 00:06:33,667
HUH?

94
00:06:33,700 --> 00:06:36,800
- THAT GATE
HAS A SPELL ON IT.
- IT DOES?

95
00:06:36,833 --> 00:06:39,233
OH, CRAP. IT REACTED TO ME.

96
00:06:39,267 --> 00:06:41,567
[ WHIMPERS ]
G-GO AWAY, YOU DEMON.

97
00:06:41,600 --> 00:06:44,400
[ GROWLS ]
WATCH WHO YOU'RE CALLING
A DEMON!

98
00:06:44,433 --> 00:06:48,267
DON'T JUMP TO CONCLUSIONS.
I'M NOT A DEMON, GOT IT?

99
00:06:48,300 --> 00:06:49,700
[ WHIMPERS, SCREAMS ]

100
00:06:49,733 --> 00:06:51,200
STAY AWAY!

101
00:06:51,233 --> 00:06:55,233
- UH, HEY.
- DON'T COME NEAR ME!

102
00:06:55,267 --> 00:06:58,000
UM, IS SOMETHING WRONG
WITH YOUR LEGS?

103
00:06:58,033 --> 00:06:59,600
HUH?

104
00:07:04,062 --> 00:07:07,629
[ YUKIO ]
VALERIANA, HYPERICUM,
FERN, HOREHOUND.

105
00:07:07,662 --> 00:07:09,629
TWO OF EACH, PLEASE.

106
00:07:09,662 --> 00:07:14,729
UH, ONE LITER
OF C-DENSITY HOLY WATER
AND 300 GRAMS OF IRON SAND.

107
00:07:14,762 --> 00:07:17,762
OH, AND SIX DOZEN
OF THE USUAL
HOLY SILVER BULLETS.

108
00:07:17,796 --> 00:07:20,929
STOCKPILING AGAIN?
YOU ARE A GOOD CUSTOMER.

109
00:07:20,962 --> 00:07:23,962
I BURNED THROUGH
MOST OF OUR SUPPLIES
THE OTHER DAY.

110
00:07:23,996 --> 00:07:27,396
SO ANYWAY,
ABOUT YOUR DAUGHTER--
HOW IS SHIEMI DOING?

111
00:07:27,429 --> 00:07:31,129
NOT TOO GOOD.
HER LEGS ARE GETTING WORSE
EVERY DAY.

112
00:07:31,162 --> 00:07:35,162
EVERY SINGLE DOCTOR
I'VE TAKEN HER TO
CAN'T FIND ANYTHING WRONG.

113
00:07:35,196 --> 00:07:38,496
THEY ALL SAY SHE'S FINE.
THAT'S WHY I ASKED YOU TO COME.

114
00:07:38,529 --> 00:07:40,529
WHAT DOES SHIEMI
HAVE TO SAY?

115
00:07:40,562 --> 00:07:43,296
WELL, YOU MIGHT SAY WE HAD
A BIT OF A FALLING OUT.

116
00:07:43,329 --> 00:07:45,896
WE'RE NOT SPEAKING MUCH
THESE DAYS.

117
00:07:45,929 --> 00:07:49,096
HAS ANYTHING HAPPENED TO HER
THAT COULD BE DEMON RELATED?

118
00:07:49,129 --> 00:07:50,629
MM.

119
00:07:50,662 --> 00:07:53,662
MY MOTHER--
SHIEMI'S GRANDMOTHER--

120
00:07:53,696 --> 00:07:55,762
PASSED AWAY LAST WINTER.

121
00:08:00,129 --> 00:08:03,662
WHOA. THAT'S RANK.
MY EYES ARE STINGING.

122
00:08:03,696 --> 00:08:06,729
I MIX COW DUNG AND WATER
TO MAKE THE FERTILIZER.

123
00:08:06,762 --> 00:08:09,862
COW DUNG, HUH?
THANK GOODNESS
I HAD YOU AROUND.

124
00:08:09,896 --> 00:08:11,829
I NEEDED THE HOLE DUG
REALLY DEEP.

125
00:08:11,862 --> 00:08:13,429
THANK GOODNESS,
MY ASS.

126
00:08:13,462 --> 00:08:16,362
FIRST YOU CALL ME A DEMON,
AND THEN YOU START
BOSSING ME AROUND?

127
00:08:16,396 --> 00:08:20,396
WELL, I'M SORRY.
I DIDN'T MEAN IT.
I WAS JUST SCARED.

128
00:08:20,429 --> 00:08:22,529
[ SIGHS ]

129
00:08:22,562 --> 00:08:25,096
- HUH?
- CAN WE MAKE UP NOW?

130
00:08:25,129 --> 00:08:28,629
WHEN I FIRST SAW YOU,
I DIDN'T REALIZE
WHAT A GOOD PERSON YOU WERE.

131
00:08:28,662 --> 00:08:31,629
[ STAMMERS ]
WELL, ALL RIGHT.

132
00:08:31,662 --> 00:08:34,362
IF YOU REALLY WANT TO,
I DON'T MIND.

133
00:08:34,396 --> 00:08:37,896
OH, I'M GLAD.
OKAY, I CAN GO FIRST.

134
00:08:37,929 --> 00:08:42,262
- I'M SHIEMI MORIYAMA.
- RIN. RIN OKUMURA.

135
00:08:42,296 --> 00:08:45,162
[ GASPS ]
<i>SHE MIXED COW POO</i>
<i>WITH THAT HAND!</i>

136
00:08:46,829 --> 00:08:49,296
THIS IS A SPECIAL PLACE
FOR ME.

137
00:08:49,329 --> 00:08:51,129
IT'S MY GRANDMA'S GARDEN.

138
00:08:51,162 --> 00:08:54,962
I'D HELP HER WITH THE PLANTING,
AND SHE'D TEACH ME
ALL KINDS OF THINGS.

139
00:08:54,996 --> 00:09:00,062
I-- I LOVE THIS GARDEN,
AND I LOVE MY GRANDMA.

140
00:09:00,096 --> 00:09:04,862
BUT LAST WINTER,
WHILE WORKING IN THE GARDEN,
SHE HAD AN ACCIDENT AND DIED.

141
00:09:04,896 --> 00:09:09,529
I THINK WHEN SHE DIED, SHE WENT
TO THE GARDEN OF AMAHARA.

142
00:09:09,562 --> 00:09:11,296
I HOPE SO ANYWAY.

143
00:09:11,329 --> 00:09:13,029
GARDEN OF AMAHARA?

144
00:09:13,062 --> 00:09:15,162
GRANDMA SAID
IT'S A PLACE GOD CREATED...

145
00:09:15,196 --> 00:09:19,196
WHERE HE GATHERED
ALL THE PLANTS
IN THE WHOLE WORLD.

146
00:09:19,229 --> 00:09:24,829
I KNOW IT'S JUST A FAIRY TALE,
BUT IF THERE REALLY IS
A GARDEN OF AMAHARA,

147
00:09:24,862 --> 00:09:27,829
A SPECIAL PLACE WHERE I CAN GO
AND WANDER AROUND...

148
00:09:27,862 --> 00:09:31,562
LOOKING AT ALL THE PLANTS
IN THE WORLD,

149
00:09:31,596 --> 00:09:33,796
THEN I'D LIKE TO GO THERE.

150
00:09:35,162 --> 00:09:36,229
[ YUKIO ]
RIN!

151
00:09:36,262 --> 00:09:37,529
- OH.
- HUH?

152
00:09:37,562 --> 00:09:39,996
I CAN'T LET YOU
OUT OF MY SIGHT
FOR A SECOND.

153
00:09:40,029 --> 00:09:43,129
- WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?
- HE-HEY, YUKIO.

154
00:09:43,162 --> 00:09:45,362
YUKI!
"YUKI"?

155
00:09:45,396 --> 00:09:47,296
- YOU KNOW HER?
- YES.

156
00:09:47,329 --> 00:09:51,862
SHIEMI'S MOTHER RUNS THE SHOP.
I SEE HER
EVERY TIME I COME HERE.

157
00:09:51,896 --> 00:09:53,562
HOW ARE YOU DOING, SHIEMI?

158
00:09:53,596 --> 00:09:55,962
HE-HELLO, YUKI.

159
00:09:55,996 --> 00:09:57,962
WE'RE TWINS.
HE'S THE OLDER ONE.

160
00:09:57,996 --> 00:10:01,662
[ GASPS ]
BUT YOU SEEM MORE LIKE
HIS BIG BROTHER.

161
00:10:01,696 --> 00:10:04,562
TO TELL YOU THE TRUTH,
I AM MORE MATURE THAN HE IS.

162
00:10:04,596 --> 00:10:06,796
TECHNICALLY, THOUGH,
HE IS THE OLDER ONE.

163
00:10:06,829 --> 00:10:08,629
TECHNICALLY?
WHATEVER!

164
00:10:08,662 --> 00:10:12,129
SHIEMI, COME ON.
LET HIM HAVE A LOOK
AT YOUR LEGS.

165
00:10:12,162 --> 00:10:15,862
BUT, MOM, I TOLD YOU
I HAVEN'T BEEN INFECTED.

166
00:10:15,896 --> 00:10:18,696
IT'S JUST A PRECAUTION.
IF I DON'T FIND ANYTHING,

167
00:10:18,729 --> 00:10:21,296
YOU'RE NONE THE WORSE OFF,
RIGHT?

168
00:10:21,329 --> 00:10:23,496
WILL YOU LET ME TAKE A LOOK?

169
00:10:23,529 --> 00:10:24,962
MM-HMM.

170
00:10:26,096 --> 00:10:27,729
IT'S OKAY.

171
00:10:32,496 --> 00:10:34,796
- A ROOT.
- [ RIN ] HUH?

172
00:10:34,829 --> 00:10:37,262
IT'S A TEMPTAINT.
A DEMON CAUSED THIS.

173
00:10:37,296 --> 00:10:40,862
- BUT THAT CAN'T BE.
- SHE'S NOT POSSESSED,
IS SHE?

174
00:10:40,896 --> 00:10:43,162
NO. SHE'S DEFINITELY
NOT POSSESSED.

175
00:10:43,196 --> 00:10:46,962
THE DEMON THAT DID THIS
ISN'T STRONG ENOUGH
TO POSSESS A HUMAN.

176
00:10:46,996 --> 00:10:50,529
THIS LOOKS LIKE THE WORK
OF A DOÖKKÁLFAR--
A GREEN MAN...

177
00:10:50,562 --> 00:10:52,196
OR AN ENT.

178
00:10:52,229 --> 00:10:55,629
THEY'RE LOW-LEVEL DEMONS
THAT POSSESS GRASS AND TREES.

179
00:10:55,662 --> 00:11:00,562
ONE OF THEM REACHED THROUGH
THE SOIL INTO SHIEMI'S LEGS
AND IS FEEDING OFF HER SOUL.

180
00:11:00,596 --> 00:11:04,462
THE DEMON IS SOMEWHERE
IN THIS GARDEN.

181
00:11:04,496 --> 00:11:06,062
[ WHIMPERS ]

182
00:11:06,096 --> 00:11:09,129
SHIEMI, USUALLY A DEMON
CAN FIND ITS WAY...

183
00:11:09,162 --> 00:11:11,929
INTO A PERSON'S SOUL
THROUGH CONVERSATION.

184
00:11:11,962 --> 00:11:14,029
YOU MUST HAVE SPOKEN
WITH ONE.

185
00:11:14,062 --> 00:11:15,362
[ WHIMPERS ]

186
00:11:15,396 --> 00:11:17,029
CAN YOU REMEMBER
DOING THAT?

187
00:11:17,062 --> 00:11:20,896
NO. I DIDN'T.
I NEVER SPOKE WITH ANY DEMON.

188
00:11:20,929 --> 00:11:24,762
SHIEMI! WE HAVE TO GET YOU
OUT OF THIS GARDEN NOW!

189
00:11:24,796 --> 00:11:28,896
I KNOW YOUR GRANDMOTHER
LOVED IT, BUT THIS HAS GONE
FAR ENOUGH, YOUNG LADY.

190
00:11:28,929 --> 00:11:32,296
I WON'T LET YOU RISK YOUR HEALTH
OVER THIS CURSED PLACE.

191
00:11:32,329 --> 00:11:34,929
THIS GARDEN ISN'T CURSED.

192
00:11:34,962 --> 00:11:38,096
THIS PLACE WAS GRANDMA'S
GREATEST TREASURE.

193
00:11:38,129 --> 00:11:41,496
I WON'T LEAVE IT, MOM!
I HATE YOU!

194
00:11:41,529 --> 00:11:43,462
[ GASPS ]

195
00:11:43,496 --> 00:11:46,129
OH, SHIEMI!
SHIEMI!

196
00:12:02,013 --> 00:12:03,780
[ GRANDMOTHER ]
GOOD, SHIEMI.

197
00:12:03,813 --> 00:12:08,313
NOW HERE'S ANOTHER TIP.
YOU PLANT ROOT VEGETABLES
WHEN THE MOON WAXES,

198
00:12:08,346 --> 00:12:10,713
AND LEAFY PLANTS
WHEN THE MOON WANES.

199
00:12:10,746 --> 00:12:14,680
- GOT IT.
- YOU REALLY LOVE
PLANTS AND FLOWERS,

200
00:12:14,713 --> 00:12:17,013
- DON'T YOU, SHIEMI?
- MM-HMM.

201
00:12:17,046 --> 00:12:19,513
AND I LOVE YOU TOO.
DON'T FORGET.

202
00:12:19,546 --> 00:12:21,480
I'LL STAY WITH YOU FOREVER.

203
00:12:23,180 --> 00:12:25,680
WITH YOU... FOREVER.

204
00:12:27,213 --> 00:12:29,580
EVEN THOUGH SHE LOOKS FINE
ON THE OUTSIDE,

205
00:12:29,613 --> 00:12:32,546
THE DEMON IS DRAINING
HER ENERGY
THROUGH HER LEGS.

206
00:12:32,580 --> 00:12:36,746
IF IT ISN'T EXORCISED SOON,
SHE WILL DIE.

207
00:12:36,780 --> 00:12:39,546
[ YUKIO ]
WHY IS SHE SLEEPING OUT
HERE IN THE STOREHOUSE?

